---
title: Vegetarian Bibimbap with Mushrooms, Carrot and Sesame Spinach
description: Grain bowls are having something of a moment lately, popping up everywhere from trendy restaurants to social media feeds. Korea perfected the art of the rice bowl way before snapping smartphone photos of your dinner ever became a thing. At its most basic, the dish consists of rice topped with a variety of veggies, proteins, and a red pepper sauce.
